                        <td align="left" colspan="1" style="background-color:white;color: black;font-size:1.1em;color: #005188;">&nbsp;Eudaly
                            Rule Would Order Portland Police To Stop Cooperating With Federal Officer</td>
                        <td align="right" style="background-color:white;font-size:1.1em;color:#005188; padding-right:8px;">Jul 22
                            2020&nbsp;04:53AM PT&nbsp;</td>
                    </tr>
