                        <td align="left" colspan="1" style="background-color:white;color: black;font-size:1.1em;color: #005188;">&nbsp;I Know
                            How to Cover a Portland Protest. So Why Am I Shaking?</td>
                        <td align="right" style="background-color:white;font-size:1.1em;color:#005188; padding-right:8px;">Jul 22
                            2020&nbsp;07:24PM PT&nbsp;</td>
