                        <td style="background-color:white;white-space:nowrap;color:black;font-size:1.0em;">&nbsp;</td>
                        <td align="right" valign="middle" colspan="3"><a id="" style="display: inline; text-decoration: none; float:right; vertical-align:middle;" href="https://www1.newsdataservice.com/NDSCheckLink.aspx?V=1&amp;P=12Kl27rXHSzSHWGl*jpR*lpCpAmK*SnWT8myjAOyj1nDT85WT8zWTRzGpC4ydR6baAzX_A4yjSKYTRxGxSKBaDKC_AnyID5vx3KqpRIidWJ72WxS(VISp70Yr7pX2X_frRIid7Ifr7pX2X6D_AzDp*5JpSpX2XKGxS6qoCyWpC0yaR6baAzX_A4b08_D_DpX2XpX2XOW2XHeZDzO*UMv*37y2RKbp2IhxChRjUq0qC0WThpPrSzY27qk2VHS*WpyI70X(VKP2Wxl28IP2W_zdWJ7p7rkrW_z(RXDpCURdVskr7JlaWv7rRyS*8Hip7wzdVyS(WKY(VyC(2" onclick="" target="_blank"><span style="color: #849f20;cursor: pointer;text-decoration: none;vertical-align: middle;font-size:0.833em;font-weight:700;">View</span><img style="width:11px; height:14px;cursor: pointer; border-style:none;vertical-align: middle;" alt="View Icon" src="https://www1.newsdataservice.com/images/Icon2ArrowRightGreen.png">&nbsp;&nbsp;</a>
